OL,6,F"That didn't materialise. I never got
OL,7,Fthose. Those individuals subsequently
OL,8,Fwent to the BBC but had they come to
OL,9,Fme a year earlier, and said to me
OL,10,F'This is me, this is my story, this is
OL,11,Fwhat happened', I would have been in a
OL,12,Fvery different situation."
OL,14,FThe report by the Welsh government's
OL,15,Fdirector of ethics and propriety,
OL,16,FDavid Richards, said: "The deputy
OL,17,Fminister should not have said in her
OL,18,Finterview that she had not been given
OL,19,Fnames by the Member for Gower, since
OL,20,Fthat was not correct".
