OL,6,FThe report goes on to state: "In my
OL,7,Fview the misstatement from the deputy
OL,8,Fminister about names does not amount
OL,9,Fto untruthfulness or constitutes a
OL,10,Fbreach of the Ministerial Code.
OL,12,F"I do not think that the deputy
OL,13,Fminister was deliberately trying to
OL,14,Fmislead and I think that the thrust of
OL,15,Fwhat the deputy minister said in her
OL,16,Finterview was an honest representation
OL,17,Fof the exchanges which she had with
OL,18,Fthe Member for the Gower.
